snippet.textDisplay:
Dear David and his team,


I understand that this may never be read but in case it does... I was thinking about writing this and then I put it off, and then I decided that I am going to do it. I rarely ever post comments. I've been watching you guys for the past few months and I cannot express how happy I am that I found about you and your channel. You guys truly make me smile and drop a few tears.. Also, you probably won't believe this, but after finding out you and Natalie graduated from Vernon Hills High School, I thought to myself "Oh my god". Reason so because I live in Grayslake which is about 20-25 mins away from Vernon Hills.. (for those who have 0 no idea, I'm sure you know David haha) I graduated in 2018 and currently am 21. Also, I was born in Riga, Latvia which I'm almost positive Dom knows exactly where that is. I've also experienced severe bullying while I was still in Latvia which has shaped me for I am today and I can assure you I can relate to Verdon's problems with kids at school (sorry if I mispronounced it). I've lived in Grayslake all the years I've been in the states and I recently acquired citizenship for which I am grateful for. So with this being said, I know you guys come to Vernon Hills to visit friends and family, and I think it would absolutely awesome to meet you and your team in person...I think it would be awesome to share stories with you guys and maybe have some content for the vlogs haha. The only thing I don't know is how we would communicate about this if this was to happen.. All in all, I fully support you and your guys' crazy ideas.. Watching you guys have fun and enjoy life is what makes me smile and admire the commitment you have for yourself and your team. Thank you David! :)
